calc_tad

calc_tad.Rd

Calculate time after dose (TAD). Records before the first dose are output < 0. For infusions (dur>0 or rate>0), the time after the end of infusion is calculated.

Usage

calc_tad(id, time, amt = NULL, evid = NULL, rate = NULL, dur = NULL)

Arguments

id

Subject identifiers values

time

Time values

amt

Amount values

evid

Event identifiers values

rate

Rate values

dur

Duration values

Examples


data_501 |>
  dplyr::mutate(TAD2 = calc_tad(id = ID, time = TIME, amt = AMT)) |>
  dplyr::select(ID, TIME, AMT, TAD2)
